08:35.740 --> 08:42.900
All his ethical philosophy and his passive virtue might turn out to be idle words if you were once exposed to the rude realities of human existence

08:44.560 --> 08:50.420
Fine thoughts and moral dissertations from men who have not worked and suffered may be read, but they will be forgotten

08:51.180 --> 08:59.120
No religion no ethical philosophy is worth anything if the teacher has not lived the quote life of an apostle end quote

08:59.120 --> 09:03.280
