For it is according to nature and nothing is evil that is according to nature

12:30.500 --> 12:31.540
end quote

12:31.540 --> 12:39.600
The physics of Antoninus is the knowledge of the nature of the universe of its government and of the relation of man's nature to both

12:40.260 --> 12:47.420
He names the universe quote the universal substance end quote and he adds that quote reason end quote

