13:12.680 --> 13:19.780
He's still on other occasion plainly distinguishes between matter material things and cause origin reason

13:19.780 --> 13:27.620
This is conformable to Zeno's doctrine that there are two original principles of all things that which acts and that which is acted upon

13:28.300 --> 13:33.600
